  "text": "Each of the previous muon decay global analyses [4, 9, [CITATION_1] 11] utilized the same input parameters -ρ, δ, P µ ξδ/ρ, ξ ′ , ξ ′′ , α/A, β/A, α ′ /A, β ′ /A. For each of these quantities, the previous analyses adopted the single most precise experimental measurement that was available at the time.",
